============
Django-SIFAC
============

This library is not really a django specific app for SIFAC but it's easy to use
with Django.
For the moment, data on cost centers, eotp, funds and functional domains is
acessible, but only for reading, not writing

Installation
------------

    pip install django-sifac


Integrate with your django app
------------------------------

You need to add this lines to the settings file of your django project ::

    ASHOST = '' #  Hostname to connect (i.e sap.host.com)
    SYSNR = '' # System number to connect to (i.e '00')
    CLIENT = '' # Client number logged in (i.e '500')
    USER = '' # Username
    PASSWF = '' # Password


